{
  "texts": [
    "This CNN extracts feature maps that represent the hierarchical properties of the input image [3, 7].",
    "• Default Box Assignment: At each position in the feature maps, default boxes of different aspect ratios are assigned.",
    "The SSD model then makes predictions for each of these default boxes, allowing it to handle objects of different shapes and sizes [3, 7].",
    "• Prediction: For each default box, the SSD model simultaneously predicts the bounding box offsets and class scores.",
    "The bounding box offsets adjust the dimensions of the default box to better fit the actual location and size of the object."
  ]
}